<taxonomicName id="2ECF4D5E3F67FFF0FE9EF887FD6AF8FA" box="[383,650,1793,1819]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiidae" genus="Pomatoschistus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="quagga">
<emphasis id="DBBBEACF3F67FFF0FE9EF887FD6AF8FA" box="[383,650,1793,1819]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">Pomatoschistus quagga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="2ECF4D5E3F67FFF0FD79F884FD0EF8FA" authorityName="Miller" authorityYear="1982" box="[664,750,1793,1819]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Gobiidae" genus="Pomatoschistus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bathi">
<emphasis id="DBBBEACF3F67FFF0FD79F884FD0EF8FA" box="[664,750,1793,1819]" italics="true" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">P. bathi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E97036DD3F67FFF0FF26F8A3FC55F885" blockId="82.[151,1436,1433,1964]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">
Habitat. Pelagic and neritic species, recorded over coarse sand, muddy sand or partially sand covered bedrock from 
<quantity id="2E379B383F67FFF0FF34F8CFFEDFF885" box="[213,319,1865,1892]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.125" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="0.25" pageId="82" pageNumber="83" unit="m" value="11.25" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="2.5">2.5–20 m</quantity>
depth (Miller 1986; 
